      "rationale": "Navier-Stokes equations with Carreau-Yasuda viscosity model selected. SST k-omega turbulence closure applied; sensitivity to turbulence model evaluated by comparison with k-epsilon results (< 3% difference in HI). Multiple reference frame approach used for impeller rotation. Model form uncertainty estimated at ±5% of HI based on turbulence model sensitivity study."
